Uses of Interface
GxExpressions.GxExpressionInterface

  • Packages that use GxExpressionInterface 
    Package Description
    GxExpressions
    The package exports a collection of predefined expression which can be used directly in columns.

    • Uses of GxExpressionInterface in GxExpressions

      Classes in GxExpressions that implement GxExpressionInterface 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  GxExpression
      Expressions are Javascript functions which are written as strings.
      class  GxExpressionAbstract
      Abstract implementation for GxExpressionInterface
      class  GxExpressionBytesFormatter
      The class defines a grid expression to format bytes to one of the following measuring terms : ['KB', 'MB', 'GB', 'TB', 'PB', 'EB', 'ZB', 'YB']
      class  GxExpressionDatesFormatter
      Deprecated. 
      Use GxExpressionDateTimesFormatter

      The class defines a grid expression to format date/timestamps according to BBj supported masks
      class  GxExpressionNumbersFormatter
      The class defines a grid expression to format numbers according to BBj supported masks
      class  GxExpressionStringsFormatter
      The class defines a grid expression to format strings according to BBj supported masks

      Alias for GxExpressionDateTimesFormatter
